translation[11]{c,v,t}:
  21,102,Uski sarsarahat tak na sunenge aur woh hamesha hamesha apni mann bhati cheezon ke darmiyan rahenge
  21,103,"Woh intihayi ghabrahat ka waqt unko zara pareshan na karega, aur malaika badh kar unko haathon haath lenge ke “yeh tumhara wahi din hai jiska tumse waada kiya jaata tha”"
  21,104,"Woh din jabke aasman ko hum yun lapeit kar rakh denge jaise tumar mein awraaq lapeit diye jatey hain (leaves of paper are rolled up in a written scroll) jis tarah pehle humne takhleeq ki ibtida ki thi usi tarah hum phir uska iaada (originate) karenge. Yeh ek wada hai hamare zimme, aur yeh kaam humein bahr-haal karna hai"
  21,105,Aur Zaboor mein hum naseehat ke baad yeh likh chuke hain ke zameen ke waris hamare neik banday hongey
  21,106,Is mein ek badi khabar hai ibadat guzar logon ke liye
  21,107,"(Aey Muhammad), humne jo tumko bheja hai to yeh dar-asal duniya walon ke haqq mein hamari rehmat hai"
  21,108,"Insey kaho, “mere paas jo wahee aati hai woh yeh hai ke tumhara khuda sirf ek khuda hai, phir kya tum sar-e-itaat jhukate ho?”"
  21,109,Agar woh mooh pherein to kehdo “maine alal-ailaan (openly) tumko khabardaar kardiya hai. Ab yeh main nahin jaanta ke woh cheez jiska tumse wada kiya jaa raha hai qareeb hai ya door
  21,110,Allah woh baatein bhi jaanta hai jo ba-awaaz buland kahi jati hain aur woh bhi jo tum chupa kar karte ho
  21,111,Main to yeh samajhta hoon ke shayad yeh (dair/delay) tumhare liye ek fitna hai aur tumhein ek waqt e khaas tak ke liye mazay karne ka mauqa diya jaa raha hai”
  21,112,"(aakhi-e-kaar) Rasool ne kaha “aey mere Rubb, haqq ke saath faisla karde, aur logon, tum jo baatein banate ho unke muqable mein hamara Rubb-e-Rehman hi hamare liye madad ka sahara hai.”"